CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season"
TitMainTitle: Four men, and four women, possibly including Claudell Mull standing on left, gathered around picnic table with Pepsi Cola, beer, and liquor bottles for Junior Mothers night picnic at Lovuola's Farm during FROGS week
